                     <interp inst="t18480515-1239-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>, stealing 1 coat, 1 pair of trowsers, and 1 waistcoat, value 50<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18480515-name-359" type="victimName">
